Titolo: Shadow Knights

Anno: 1991

Descrizione: Shadow Knights - The Shogun of Death (Also known as "Budo - The Art of Ninja Combat") is a platform game created by id Software and published by Softdisk in 1991. Shadow Knights was the first game created for Softdisk, who paid $5000 for it as part of id Software's contractual obligation to them. Shadow Knights was also marketed by Softdisk as part of "The Lost Game Collection of ID Software".